tickets.title: Unable to Login
tickets.body: I have been trying to log into my account but I keep receiving an error message that says 'Invalid credentials'. I have double-checked my username and password, but the issue persists. Could you please help me resolve this problem as I urgently need to access my account to complete a project? Thank you.

tickets.title: Password Reset Link Not Working
tickets.body: I attempted to reset my password using the 'Forgot Password' option, but the link I received in the email is not working. It leads me to a blank page, and I have tried it multiple times. Please assist me in resetting my password so I can log into my account again. It's crucial that I regain access as soon as possible.

tickets.title: Feature Request: Dark Mode
tickets.body: I love using your platform, but I was wondering if it would be possible to introduce a 'dark mode' option. I often work late at night, and the bright screen strains my eyes. A dark mode feature would make the platform much easier to use in low-light environments. I'd really appreciate it if you could consider this feature request.

tickets.title: Error 404 on Documentation Page
tickets.body: Whenever I try to access the documentation page for API integration, I encounter a '404 Not Found' error. I have tried clearing my browser cache and even used different browsers, but the issue remains the same. I need access to the documentation to complete my integration tasks. Please fix this issue or provide me with an alternative way to access the documentation.

tickets.title: Billing Error - Charged Twice
tickets.body: I noticed that I have been charged twice for my recent subscription renewal. I initially thought it was a mistake on my part, but after reviewing my account, I can confirm that I was billed twice for the same service period. Please look into this issue and process a refund for the extra charge. Let me know if you need any further information from my side.

tickets.title: Let me now sleep
tickets.body: it is time i went to bed so i can wake up early and do some sports
